OL,3,CCharities concerned over limiting
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payments as energy prices
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThe increase in the energy price cap
OL,8,Fcomes as the Government removes winter
OL,9,Ffuel payments for about 10 million
OL,10,Fpensioners.
OL,12,FThe Government announced in July it
OL,13,Fwould issue payments only to pension
OL,14,Fcredit recipients or claimants of some
OL,15,Fother means-tested benefits, including
OL,16,Funiversal credit.
OL,18,FAbout 10 million people will lose the
OL,19,Fallowance this year.
