OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThe annual tax-free payment of between
OL,8,F#100 and #300 was introduced in 1997
OL,9,Fto help eligible pensioners meet the
OL,10,Fcosts of heating their homes in winter.
OL,12,FThe number of people who received the
OL,13,Fpayment last winter was 214,000 more
OL,14,Fthan the 11.4 million in 2022-23, and
OL,15,Fit has steadily risen from 11.1
OL,16,Fmillion in 2020-21, statistics
OL,17,Freleased by the Department for Work
OL,18,Fand Pensions (DWP) show.
