OL,7,FDelegates at Labour's annual
OL,8,Fconference backed a union motion
OL,9,Fcalling for the cut to be reversed,
OL,10,Falthough the vote is not binding on
OL,11,Fthe Government and ministers have made
OL,12,Fit clear the policy will not be
OL,13,Fchanged.
