OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat Treasury spokeswoman
OL,8,FDaisy Cooper said: "Today's price rise
OL,9,Fwill be a crushing blow to all those
OL,10,Fpensioners who are wondering how they
OL,11,Fwill get through the coming months
OL,12,Fwithout having to choose between
OL,13,Fheating and eating, after the winter
OL,14,Ffuel payment cuts.
OL,16,F"It is not too late for the Government
OL,17,Fto think again and ensure vulnerable
OL,18,Fpensioners get the support they need."
