OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FCaroline Abrahams, charity director at
OL,8,FAge UK, said restricting the winter
OL,9,Ffuel payment to those on pension
OL,10,Fcredit was "reckless and wrong" and
OL,11,F"spells disaster for pensioners on low
OL,12,Fand modest incomes".
OL,14,FMeans testing the winter fuel payment
OL,15,Fis expected to save the Government
OL,16,F#1.4 billion this year, which Labour
OL,17,Fsaid was necessary to make up the gap
OL,18,Fbetween the previous government's
OL,19,Fspending plans and the money that was
OL,20,Fmade available to fund them.
