OL,7,FLabour has also criticised the
OL,8,Fprevious government for failing to
OL,9,Finvest in energy efficiency and
OL,10,Frenewable power.
OL,12,FThe Government also said that more
OL,13,Fthan one million pensioners would
OL,14,Fstill receive the winter fuel payment,
OL,15,Fand urged any pensioner worried about
OL,16,Fthe impact of higher bills to check if
OL,17,Fthey are eligible for pension credit.
