OL,7,FAndy Manning, head of energy policy at
OL,8,FCitizens Advice, said: "This price
OL,9,Frise means bills are now around two-
OL,10,Fthirds higher than before the energy
OL,11,Fcrisis.
OL,13,F"With record levels of energy debt,
OL,14,Fthe removal of previous support and
OL,15,Fchanges to the eligibility of the
OL,16,Fwinter fuel payment, people are in
OL,17,Fdesperate need.
