OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"The Government must urgently
OL,8,Fintroduce targeted bill support that
OL,9,Freflects the realities of people's
OL,10,Fenergy needs."
OL,12,FSimon Francis, co-ordinator of the End
OL,13,FFuel Poverty Coalition, said: "We're
OL,14,Fnow heading into the fourth winter of
OL,15,Fsky high energy prices.
