OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"After October 1, bills will be 65%
OL,8,Fhigher than in 2020/21, meaning the
OL,9,Faverage household will have paid more
OL,10,Fthan #2,500 extra for their energy
OL,11,Fthan had we not been so exposed to
OL,12,Fvolatile energy markets.
OL,14,F"For older people who previously
OL,15,Freceived the winter fuel payment, but
OL,16,Fwill no longer do so under the
OL,17,FChancellor's new rules, the situation
OL,18,Fis even worse. For many pensioners,
OL,19,Fthis winter will feel like the most
OL,20,Fexpensive on record.
