OL,7,F"What's worse, there are more price
OL,8,Fincreases on the horizon.
OL,10,F"We welcome the Government's long-term
OL,11,Fplans to boost home energy efficiency
OL,12,Fto bring down bills and to improve
OL,13,Fenergy security to stabilise prices,
OL,14,Fbut these reforms will take time to
OL,15,Ftake effect and will be cold comfort
OL,16,Fto those struggling this winter.
