OL,7,F"That's why it is so vital the
OL,8,Fministers bring in more support for
OL,9,Fvulnerable households this winter,
OL,10,Freductions in standing charges and a
OL,11,Fsocial tariff.
OL,13,F"The energy industry has made more
OL,14,Fthan #457 billion in profit since the
OL,15,Fstart of the crisis, so there is
OL,16,Fplenty of money in the system to be
OL,17,Fable to ensure everyone stays warm
OL,18,Fthis winter and next."
